Named formattingLocale the following:var locales = {
  en: {
    message: {
      hello: '{msg} world'
    }
  }
}
Template the following:{{ $t('message.hello', { msg: 'hello' }) }}
Output the following:hello world
List formattingLocale the following:var locales = {
  en: {
    message: {
      hello: '{0} world'
    }
  }
}
Template the following:{{ $t('message.hello', ['hello']) }}
Output the following:hello world
Support ruby on rails i18n formatLocale the following:var locales = {
  en: {
    message: {
      hello: '%{msg} world'
    }
  }
}
Template the following:{{ $t('message.hello', { msg: 'hello' }) }}
Output the following:hello world
